他们带入梦乡。 \r\n　　宁静祥和的乡村之夜，壁火熊熊燃烧，母亲正在缝制针线活，小男孩则快乐地敲着铁皮鼓走来走去。突然，挂钟敲响八下，孩子的睡觉时间到了，小男孩不情愿地接过母亲手中的煤油灯，独自上楼睡觉。黑暗的楼梯对他来说是一条漫长恐怖的路程，而幽冷的长夜更让男孩惴惴不安。 \r\n　　这时，一个长相怪异、体形消瘦的怪物闪身进屋，一步步向男孩的房间走去……","name":"The Sandman","name_cn":"睡仙","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"英国","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短篇","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1991","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Berry","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黑暗向","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Paul","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"定格动画","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"睡仙"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"El cuco"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1991-01-02"},{"key":"片长","value":"10分钟"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"www.screenonline.org.uk/film/id/792073/"},{"key":"IMDb链接","value":"tt0105311"},{"key":"制片国家/地区","value":"英国"},{"key":"语言","value":"英语"},{"key":"导演","value":"Paul Berry"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":17,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":4,"6":6,"7":4,"8":1,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.9},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":4,"wish":6,"collect":33,"doing":1},"id":129596,"eps":1,"meta_tags":[],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1991-01-01","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/2c/58/551283_Zqkwo.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/2c/58/551283_Zqkwo.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/2c/58/551283_Zqkwo.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/2c/58/551283_Zqkwo.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/2c/58/551283_Zqkwo.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"요정핑크","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"韩国","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"英文名","v":"Fairy Pink"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"放送开始",